item.title: About
item.description: Hi, I’m Hans Ollivander (han5 011ivand3r). I am a student and dreamer. As a student, I ask questions and seek for digestible answers. Generally, it is followed by me trying to contradict my brain with wrong answers. And a dreamer, because that’s where freedom is. I am passionate about human space exploration, machine learning and storytelling. I often find myself dabbling in the reality of fickleness of carbon-based life on planet Earth.
